data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 3 bed 3 bath ranch home situated on a large corner lot in Hampton Station. Features a huge family room with vaulted ceilings and a gas log fireplace. Large fenced in backyard and much more. The Master bedroom features a beautiful trey ceiling with crown molding, an en suite bath with a whirlpool tub, and stand alone shower and massive walk in closet. Comes with an additional oversized office. The kitchen features beautiful cabinetry with an eat in area and easy access to a spacious dining room.  Walking distance to community pool & new Mark Russel Center. Only minutes away from Bailey Cove and Hampton Cove shopping centers.
